Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有別的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是艾紐．雷特納爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能確信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不那麼做 萊爾．狄蘭提就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯．阿勒威也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也被什麼附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和以前不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦內需進行系統檢查 暫時切斷電源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查完畢 恢復通常電源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操縱系統 恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 敵方艦隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可視領城內似乎沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難保不會像之前一樣用些卑鄙手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系統當機時似乎收到了緊急暗號通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只寫了宙域坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐標是L5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建設停工狀態的殖民衛星 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去L5？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方只發了坐標過來 你都打算回應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是剎那堅持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避難的琳達她們也在L5繼續進行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話或許能拿到之前構思的新裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那裡之前還能進行Gundam的修理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我操縱艦船？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞負傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須有人守護托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讓我上戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應過史米盧佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪．比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續戰鬥的話 總有一天你也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密迂迴 吸引敵方注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們趁機接觸發信人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去救人吧 那我就幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前對不住了 我太衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格做Meister了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉那些變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是以Katharon的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是作為天人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要以自己的意志打敗他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 第1第3艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射時機交給00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00 剎那．F．清英 出動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 沙慈．庫斯洛德 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 合體模式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser 向L5飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝影機捕捉到天人的宇航船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在改變航向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要打敗天人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能打擊反對勢力的士氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為所欲為的特許員已經靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不負片桐司令的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要用壓倒性的兵力擊潰他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 連艾紐都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是變革者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歸我了 00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那戰鬥方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是MS性能高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00的機師開始革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則解釋不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想說他是純種？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會成為人類首個變革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型MA的修理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你別管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和准尉收到了特別命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去請求古德曼准將批准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是別以為跟得上我和准尉的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離到達目標地點需要幾日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 你要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替沒能改變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論前方有何結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席琳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好在你也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和聯邦軍政變派的倖存者接觸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在支部幾乎都被毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在地上太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是宇宙中Katharon的兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不悲觀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也有人正以和我們或天人不同的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表達自己的主張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這歌是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 瑪莉娜皇女的歌正在廣為傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜的歌傳向了世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們都在追求和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過瑪莉娜皇女的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消除紛爭 共同生存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一味否定人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許迷失了人類相互理解的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互理解的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜一直追求這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信著那前方的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指定坐標無人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 天人真的會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若他們不來世界就是變革者的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被利馮茲．阿爾馬克據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜．崔尼蒂是幾時倒戈向變革者的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別老問我 自己想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你這樣 我才被迫成為王家當主的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為兄長你沒有當權的器量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生才被扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才希望世界變革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭上一切地位 名譽 資產
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我要重新開始人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住只屬於我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得陪我到最後 紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有這個責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這理由還真夠婆婆媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是有夠笨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜．崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最不齒你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最不齒你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還裝帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不追嗎 不追嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣計劃會加速進展
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既非伊奧利亞也不是利馮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS無法抵達指定坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體控制交還你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王留美？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有Veda本體的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的本體？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被變革者知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda會被轉移走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡早奪回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我們離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法與你們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4年不見了 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年 如果不想失去Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能回應我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人格拉漢姆．艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欲與你公平決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是利馮茲指使的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼盼望決一勝負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你玷污我的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪走同胞與恩師的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踐踏我們Flag機師自尊心的並非別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是你和Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這已經超越了愛憎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為宿命！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宿命？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想笑我單方面強加於人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 別忘記最先開始武力介入的是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡又有一個被我們逼瘋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我接受決鬥邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 控制權轉到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要打？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這便是我嚮往的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修羅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨修羅生．須佐之男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公平…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人也好 變革者也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都必須像哥哥那樣獻出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終成就變革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要見證其後美好的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就別敝夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早說了 我最不齒你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服從你不過是為活命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給點好臉色你就信以為真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是把人當東西使喚的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為了生存不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我活得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這也是我服從變革者的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥們的仇還沒報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時看我一口咬斷他的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅自行動者必須給予懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審判你的人即將出現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審判人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 哥哥們的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 某種意義上是仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是它 是那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死了媽媽和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台機體是Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死路易斯家人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 路易斯．阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的復仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說過要使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為家人報仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又何嘗不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為天下就你最可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被製造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被送上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎能死在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…媽媽和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連這都沒能來得及說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throne被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不集中精力戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道和Gundam在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准尉的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了 媽媽爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你們報仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打敗了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸 你們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了 終於做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誇誇我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誇我做的好…說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍辱偷生…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為這一刻忍辱偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便淪落為變革者的掌中傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯有這武士道！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不惜這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難分勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.98,0:22:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經身在涅槃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是量子彙集的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘀咕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞．舒恩伯格製造Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 製造GN Driver的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入是為此鋪路的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的目的是將人類引導至新紀元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面臨變革
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人對A-LAWS實施強襲作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 為了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使身背罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要這場戰鬥能夠贏得未來…
